Author: feiturdrengur
Text: Anybody who tells me to stop eating popcorn is dead to me. In my opinion telling someone with bulimia or BED to just "eat some fruit" isn't very helpful at all. Is she specialized in eating disorders? Maybe it's time to shop around for someone you feel comfortable with.

Author: uwuchris
Text: Sounds like you should stop paying her... I'm not a professional, but that seems like very unhealthy advice.
